description: Mikhuna is making LA foodies’ delicious dreams come true with their absolutely scrumptious Peruvian food. Their menu features an authentic selection of sandwiches with your choice of meat (roasted chicken, turkey, or chicharron) served on brioche buns, with lettuce, special aji sauce (for the perfect zing), and marinated red onions. You’ll also find classic dishes like their Saltado plates; your choice of chicken or beef, stir fried with onions & tomatoes, and served with french fries, green beans, and savory garlic rice. For all this and much, much more, make your way straight to Mikhuna.
name: Mikhuna
